{
  "stem": "1222.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so I was slowly come around and say, momma, it's Schmilic, mama, it's Schmilic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I heared quietly, my father said to the mother, it's Schmilic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my mouth says, [NON-ENGLISH] The goyim [NON-ENGLISH] in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The Ukrainian people want to find out special.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because a lot of Ukrainians, they spoke Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I give you all kind of sign, and she had start crying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[SOBBING] My mother was so excited that she took me by the hair, and I was bleeding my head, she pulled me down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then what happened, she start bugging me, asking me, where is Rifka?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I fooled her for almost [SOBBING] three days, that Rifka's alive, and she's hiding herself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that [INAUDIBLE] Ukrainian purpose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That time they went away, they made a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put up wires around two streets, because it was left that time they slaughtered 2,200.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, was 2,000. 2,000 and-- or a little bit over 2,000.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it was left, 800 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one night, we see my mother is not in bed with [INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we all slaughtered there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, it was all that thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody leave for the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother went, runned away to the-- they were watching, but not so closely to the wires.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she walked to that Ukrainian man, and I saw it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I started running over there and watching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother was sitting by the Ukrainian man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He did not touch her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He gave her something to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she find out that the [INAUDIBLE] is there, that my sister is dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father knew about it, and my middle sister Dvoira knew about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother, I didn't want to tell her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had a weak heart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walked with her back at nighttime.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
